{
  "stem": "19895.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and I recall in our barracks the number of people were just taken away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the burial society-- burial society-- some very religious Jews, they volunteer, even today, the-- when a Jewish person dies, the Jewish burial society, people who wash the bodies and help with the burial and so on, as far as preparing the body.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were people who were volunteering their services there to help always with burying people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- they felt like that they are fulfilling some ancient Jewish law and they did it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wasn't among them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because my experience after I fainted, I-- I had a-- a tremendous fear of death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some people who were indeed praying every day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They never lost their beliefs in God.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were people whom I observed in our own barrack who-- who were praying daily.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew a lot of the prayers by heart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I murmured them, hoping that maybe somebody listens up in heaven.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had some strengths and I had some doubts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was saying morning prayers, which-- which I knew by heart.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always negotiated with my father as a child, can I start at [HEBREW] Or-- or can I start at [HEBREW]?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or can I-- can I start just at the [HEBREW]?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- I was remembering certain of those prayers pretty well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I murmured them at times of-- of-- of my own time when I thought that God may be listening to me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As I said, I had hopes, I had doubts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had hopes, I had doubts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always remembered my father's blessing that was to me, as strong as anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I will survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I hope to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I try to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
